snippet.title: MELOPAD - MP3 Rhythm Game
snippet.description:
The Best MP3 Rhythm Game!
Play MELOBEAT with your own MP3 files.
MELOBEAT can play any song on your device. It's FREE. 
DRM-protected files would not be supported.
